{"tid":1754490,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁美芬: 區選與政治掛勾，市民為表達對政府不滿而投票，希望政府深切反省。","createTime":"2019-11-25T08:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:11:12.000Z","uid":167469,"like":79,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"09c7598fd7f37775ee1efcbbf780b5a02f5b1ea5","tid":1754490,"uid":167469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:29:55.000Z","msg":"經民聯主席盧偉國表示，今屆區議會選舉派出25人參選，有3人當選，連同2名當然議席議員，來屆區議會佔5個議席，比本屆的12席少，他承認成績未如理想，感到失望，又提及在競選期間，參選人、義工及支持者，都要面對黑色恐怖的威嚇，地區辦事處無一倖免，受到不同程度破壞，甚至被掟汽油彈，情況相當嚴峻。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會議員梁美芬就指，選舉在暴力及不公平下進行，甚至出現懷疑選舉不公的情況，會保留追究權利，研究會否在相關選區作選舉呈請。梁美芬說她會尊重結果，但多位實力建制派參選人落選，顯示區選與政治掛勾，市民為表達對政府不滿而投票，希望政府深切反省。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1218194&amp;csid=261_341&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Q_jWY0blcOiLYf8sho6uWnpakv0P_aNA8aKTngWnPLHbsQYdSW1GRX1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1218194%26csid%3D261_341%26fbclid%3DIwAR3Q_jWY0blcOiLYf8sho6uWnpakv0P_aNA8aKTngWnPLHbsQYdSW1GRX1k&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJjizWcNDgH0nsvPDQhA%2BiAk%3D&h=267c4b17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1218194&amp;csid=261_341&amp;fbclid=IwAR3Q_jWY0blcOiLYf8sho6uWnpakv0P_aNA8aKTngWnPLHbsQYdSW1GRX1k</a>"},{"pid":"7232c71a0107e0caa36b3c6ed05874ef0f0ea71f","tid":1754490,"uid":185045,"like":311,"dislike":2,"score":309,"citedBy":22,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:31:42.000Z","msg":"其實想問好耐<br />\n地方選舉唔係同政治掛勾可以同咩掛勾?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99839f935f621e6609734034c57aadbd158c1cf4","tid":1754490,"uid":167469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:31:43.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"91265c650a83b651d325919405420ca37c4d2004","tid":1754490,"uid":35919,"like":49,"dislike":1,"score":48,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T08:31:54.000Z","msg